{
  "name": "stream-pipe",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "串流管線器",
  "category": "E",
  "number": 95,
  "pain_point": "大檔串流處理難",
  "commercial": "✅",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "click",
    "rich",
    "sys"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "幫我建立一個串流管線來處理大量資料",
    "設定資料處理管線，一邊讀一邊轉換",
    "不想把整個檔案載入記憶體，用串流方式處理",
    "把標準輸入的資料串流處理後輸出",
    "這個 10GB 的大檔案要怎麼流式處理",
    "建立多步驟的資料串流處理流程",
    "用管線方式處理大型日誌檔案",
    "Kafka topic 即時消費並過濾",
    "串流資料即時過濾關鍵字",
    "即時消費 Kafka 訊息邊過濾",
    "message queue 邊跑邊篩選",
    "建立串流資料處理管線"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "串流處理 large_log.txt 並過濾出 ERROR 行",
      "params": {
        "input_file": "large_log.txt",
        "filter_pattern": "ERROR",
        "action": "run"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "建立管線將 stdin 輸入轉換後寫入 output.txt",
      "params": {
        "output_file": "output.txt",
        "transform": "uppercase",
        "action": "run"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "串流讀取 data.csv 並逐行轉換格式，chunk 大小 1000",
      "params": {
        "input_file": "data.csv",
        "chunk_size": 1000,
        "output_file": "converted.json",
        "action": "run"
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "action": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "chunk_size": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "filter_pattern": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "input_file": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "output_file": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "transform": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "action"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT"
}